{"tid":1080630,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"公司星期五有同事last day","createTime":"2019-03-27T17:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T03:57:10.000Z","uid":169942,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8189356e046f25a24a32d182e42f2b9fb36a160d","tid":1080630,"uid":169942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T17:27:01.000Z","msg":"有無人同我一樣自細好怕同人分離<br />\n<br />\n由小學畢業開始 然後中學大學畢業 到今次同事last day <br />\n<br />\n分離呢種感覺 硬係唔知點形容好<br />\n<br />\n明明一個人平時會同你日日見日日吹水日日食飯 大家關係好密切 但聽日呢個人頓時就好似係你生命中消失咗咁<br />\n<br />\n我唔知點用文字先可以解釋到<br />\n<br />\n呢種又未到愛 但又足以令你唔開心同好失落嘅感覺 我好怕面對呢類友情失去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS:Stella 希望你事業發展順利 生活愉快 <br />\n<br />\n記得久晤久要搵下我地食個飯玩下呀"},{"pid":"a885d0f8aba4a50a4e57b7de7c54651a8bd7a510","tid":1080630,"uid":77320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T17:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68b0a68703cd9e087124fc6303b158702b7de38","tid":1080630,"uid":103380,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T17:36:01.000Z","msg":"初一十五去拜下佢 佢就會好開心架啦 時間沖淡一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61de0b24c04969ec3b9c89ec417c0311e7f4990","tid":1080630,"uid":169942,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"b68b0a68703cd9e087124fc6303b158702b7de38","tid":1080630,"uid":103380,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T17:36:01.000Z","msg":"初一十五去拜下佢 佢就會好開心架啦 時間沖淡一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T17:44:49.000Z","msg":"把口收吓 幫自己積吓陰得<br />\n<br />\n好好地感情台舒服吓情緒感覺 <br />\n<br />\n咁賤格好好笑有必要咩"},{"pid":"f5c1ec2fd341cc4caa84f9303f642f228a5288bf","tid":10